is class is cross listed with the following cee 175a 275a earthsys 175 275 number of units 4 course number 514 recently taught by alexandria boehm margaret meg caldwell deborah a sivas all environmental law and natural resources courses advanced environmental law clinic california coast science policy and law climate change workshop environment and energy workshop environmental law and policy environmental law clinic environmental science for managers and policy makers water law and policy related links axess coursework digital reserve sls registrar cloudy 50 f 2012 stanford university system requirements help virtual tour
